            {
               "text": "### Prerequisites\n\nIn this text, we continue studying division by three. Therefore, we recommend reading the previous text, which introduces the topic (<htcite0>).",
               "source": [
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "3c81aa4a-3030-4767-861a-25f13272776f",
                     "text": "History Tracers Team",
